These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
City: colone, venice, liverpool
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, soy-milk
1. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| City   | colone | liverpool | venice    |
| Beverage     | lemonade    | soy-milk       | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, german, indonesian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, satire, romance
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the german is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality     | indonesian | spanish | german  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | satire  | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, yellow, light-blue
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, dutch
1. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes yellow is the dutch##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Color           | light-blue | yellow | chestnut |
| Nationality   | brazilian        | dutch    | chinese        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, soul, jazz
3 different games are played: billiard, chess, backgammon
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
3. the person playing billiard is between the fan of jazz and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | soul | classical |
| Game     | chess  | billiard    | backgammon  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, apple, orange
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating apple and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Food   | apple | strawberry | orange |
| Beverage     | coffee   | sprite   | juice   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
House: craftsman, palace, townhouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, skateboard, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| House   | townhouse | craftsman | palace      |
| Transport     | skateboard  | scooter | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, july, august
City: berlin, san-francisco, paris
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday   | july  | august    | september       |
| City   | san-francisco | paris | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, scrabble
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, badminton, snowboarding
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Game   | scrabble        | snooker  | mah-jongg   |
| Sport       | snowboarding | badminton | golf |

