There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, almond-milk
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Game           | monopoly | whist | domino |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | juice | tea     |

