.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, go, canasta
3 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, dog
1. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Game      | monopoly | go    | canasta      |
| Pet   | hedgehog       | fish | dog |

