.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, baccarat
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, dahlia
1. the person who growsiris is between the dunhill-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
2. the person who growsazalea is the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Cigar      | ritmeester    | baccarat    | dunhill  |
| Flower   | azalea | iris | dahlia |

