2. the analyst is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
3. the person eating grapefruit is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Job   | accountant    | dancer   | analyst |
