.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse, goat
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, aquamarine, purple
1. the person who likes aquamarine is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes chestnut##2
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes purple is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Pet   | mouse | goat | guinea-pig |
| Color   | chestnut     | aquamarine  | purple    |

