The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, january, june
1. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
| Nationality          | spanish | pakistani    | colombian |
| Birthday   | june      | january | may  |

