.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, lawyer, fisherman
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, blue, lavender
1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
2. the lawyer is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the scientist is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Job      | fisherman    | lawyer | scientist         |
| Color   | lavender | blue  | brown |

 